General Assembly Senate Joint
Resolution No. 26
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1185
Referred to Committee on Judiciary
Introduced by:
SEN. WINFIELD, 10th Dist.
REP. STAFSTROM, 129th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF THE HONORABLE
SUSAN A. CONNORS OF OLD LYME TO BE A JUDGE OF THE
SUPERIOR COURT.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of the
2 Honorable Susan A. Connors of Old Lyme to be a Judge of the Superior
3 Court, to serve for a term of eight years from May 5, 2026, is approved
4 and confirmed, and she is appointed a Judge of the Superior Court for
5 said term.
